Lingua-tlhInganHol-yIghun!

    Allow Terran scum to program in the Warrior's Tongue!

INSTALLATION

To install this module, make sure you have Module::Build installed and
then run the following commands:

     perl Build.PL
     ./Build
     ./Build test
     ./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

    Courage
    Valour
    Strength
    Honour
    Test::More          0.88 or stronger
    Test::Harness       3.00 or stronger
    Filter::Simple


